@startuml A2_02_component_rag_service_simple
title RAG Service – Simplified View

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #000000
  BorderThickness 1
}

rectangle "RAG Service\nPort: 8080" as RAG_SERVICE {
  rectangle "Document Processing\n(ingestion pipeline)" as INGESTION
  rectangle "Query Pipeline\n(vector + graph search)" as QUERY
}

database "Postgres\n+ pgvector" as DB
database "Neo4j" as NEO4J
cloud "OpenAI\nEmbeddings" as OPENAI
cloud "Observability" as OBS

INGESTION --> OPENAI : generate embeddings
INGESTION --> DB : store vectors
INGESTION --> NEO4J : store graph
QUERY --> DB : vector search
QUERY --> NEO4J : graph query
RAG_SERVICE --> OBS

note right of RAG_SERVICE
**Role:** Stateless Data Service
**Tech:** FastAPI + LangChain
**Key Functions:**
- Policy document processing
- Vector similarity search
- Knowledge graph queries
- Hybrid retrieval
end note

@enduml

